# Data security & privacy

## Never commit or paste in chat

- Full bank account numbers, routing numbers, online banking passwords
- Full SIN, full credit card numbers, API keys, `.env` contents
- **Supabase service_role key** (bypasses all RLS)
- Client, project, time, invoice, or payment rows (Supabase only)
- `company/profile.local.md`, `company/legal-index.local.md`, `app/.env.local`
- Unredacted PDF statements (store locally; commit redacted extracts if needed)

## Redaction

- Bank statements: keep last 4 digits only in shared files.
- Employee/shareholder SIN: reference as `***-***-XXX` (last 3 only if required for matching).

## Separation

- **Corporate only** in this repo. Personal expenses paid personally → note for reimbursement; do not mix into corporate GL without owner approval.
- Credit cards: corporate card transactions only in corporate books unless explicitly reclassified.

## File handling

- Preserve original filenames in `archive/` when renaming for convention.
- Do not delete financial source documents; move superseded files to `archive/YYYY/`.

## Git

- Respect `.gitignore`. If a secret was committed, tell the owner immediately — do not rewrite history without explicit instruction.
